				Some info from my experience camping the bear.. <BR>
<BR>
I swam into cave only to find 2 skeletons wandering by,  Not knowing at the time they were the place holder for bear I ignored them, searched cave to find no bear, so I sat down and started reading about him..  Once I found out the 2 skellies were PH I ran all over searching for them,  when I saw them!  Before I could do anything they attacked me!!<BR>
<BR>
Turns out these 2 skellies I found WERE NOT the first ones I saw =(   Lich of miragul jumped me and his pet..    my pet was getting bombarded, so I sat and memmed gate, right after that I got nuked for couple hundred.. (miragul conned red, didn't con his pet)  I ran just as my pet was slaughtered..   Luckily I ran far and around lots of corners,   I got hit by a DOT : Scourge <BR>
Casted gate..<BR>
and crossed my fingers,  Made it out barely with just enough time to cast counteract disease..<BR>
<BR>
Be careful in that cave, 2 npcs that can own ya if yer not 55+ or whatever hehe<BR>
